D. Acquisition Strategy
Combat Identification develops technologies for exploitation by the United States Air Force (USAF) and other services. Award multiple, competitive contract vehicles
emphasizing the use of government owned technologies, government off-the-shelf technology (GOTS), commercial off-the-shelf (COTS), and maximize the use of non-
developmental items (NDIs). Management develops a technology to a point it can be demonstrated in a relevant operational environment.




