       The FY 2026 request was reduced by $0.078 million for Advisory and Assistance Services to promote efficiencies and advance the policies of the Administration
       in alignment with Executive Order 14222, "Implementing the President's Department of Government Efficiency Cost Efficiency Initiative."

       The FY 2026 budget for Project 1822 was reduced by $2.466M to meet demands from MyNavy HR sponsors for research related efforts supporting MPTE.




