D. Acquisition Strategy
An Ensemble Analysis was implemented in FY25 to further identify and understand counter-HDBT capability gaps and inform the Air Force and DoD acquisition strategy.
The approach for the Ensemble Analysis for HDBT defeat: 1) Synthesize current state-of-the-art, including past research and validated capability requirements, 2)
Conduct a holistic study to examine and recommend solutions for all dimensions of HDBT defeat considering nuclear, conventional, and non-kinetic effects, to include
layering of two or more of those effects, and 3) inform and drive follow-on Analyses of Alternatives to provide concrete trade space characterization and acquisition
strategy recommendations for each of the three effect categories.




