D. Acquisition Strategy
The Analysis of Alternatives (AoA) was initiated in 2QFY2022 to begin the assessment of the technical feasibility, operational feasibility, technical risk, and affordability of
potential materiel and non-materiel solutions. The AoA was completed in 1QFY2023 resulting in a recommendation for pre-Milestone A efforts and a Milestone A entry.
Limited pre-Milestone A efforts began in FY 2024. In FY 2026, program planning and Milestone A acquisition documentation efforts continue to support a Milestone A
decision.




