D. Acquisition Strategy
C-sUAS acquisition strategy will include leveraging a combination of currently funded JCO and DoD efforts, OEM production and support contracts, and Naval Warfare
engineering and organic Lead System Integrator (oLSI) capabilities. This will help maintain commonality of current C-sUAS solutions while continuing to evaluate,
improve, and implement layered defense capabilities into the integrated FoS to defeat evolving threats. To maximize resource allocations, the Program will utilize
existing DOD contracts that have been deemed appropriate for the funding, as well as award any new contracts needed.




