FY 2025 Plans:
(U) MTC funding supports the continuing research, development, integration, and test and evaluation of:
- Using agile software methodology, MTC will conduct three capability baseline iterations in FY23.
- Funding supports Extended User Evaluations where deployed prototypes are utilized to gather system
feedback, conduct CONOP development, and accomplish training iterations.
- MTC has key partnerships with other DOD and government agencies utilizing documented agreements to
collaborate, experiment, and support capability development across the targeting enterprise. Additional details
are held at a higher classification level.
