FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Increase from FY2025 to FY2026 of $43.465 million provides for Advanced Development Classified efforts
and DSSC-6 development efforts that were reduced in FY2025 due to higher funding priorities. This increase
supports DSSC-6 development as it heads into Critical Design Review (CDR) in FY2026. It also provides
